title: Predicting the Starting Quarterbacks for All 32 Teams
description:
Nora is joined by The Ringer’s Kaelen Jones and The Athletic’s Jourdan Rodrigue to play matchmaker and predict who the starting quarterbacks will be for all 32 teams in the 2021 season (3:00).
Host: Nora Princiotti
Guests: Kaelen Jones and Jourdan Rodrigue
